    How To Install Help

    If you are asking for help, provide lots of detail so problems can be reproduced.

    Things to describe:
    operating system - Windows XP Home Edition
    version of ATutor - ATutor-1.5.2.tar
    versions of php -
    version of mysq l -
    webserver & version -
    copies of error messages -
    changes to default settings -
    web browser being used - IE6
    and anything else relevant -

    Also, the file should be name ATutor-1.5.2.tar.gz. If windows has stripped off the .gz file extension, manually add it back on then try unzipping again.

    Re: How To Install??? Help!!!

    Upload it to your web site then use the following command at the command prompt

    tar xzvf ATutor-1.5.2.tar.gz

    (make sure the .gz file extension is included)
